      *%METADATA                                                       *
      * %TEXT Error Code parameter for API calls                       *
      *%EMETADATA                                                      *
     I*
     I* API Error message structure:
     I$APIER      DS
     I I            80                    B   1   40$ERSIZ
     I* $ERSIZ = bytes provided for error data; controls error handling:
     I* 0 => API control; errors cause program to abend.
     I* 8 or more => this program will handle errors (like MONMSG).
     I I            0                     B   5   80$ERLEN
     I* $ERLEN = bytes of error data returned by the API.  If it is
     I* > 0, an error occurred.
     I                                        9  15 $ERMIC
     I* If $ERMIC is blank, the API completed successfully; if it fails
     I* the error message ID for the reason will be in $ERMIC.
     I                                       16  16 $ERRSV
     I* Bytes 17 through $ERSIZ contain the replacement text for $ERMIC.
     I                                       17  96 $ERTXT
     I*
